{"id":283837,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-丁红芬获释后仍受监视，她将申请政府信/","date":"2013-03-13T09:45:39Z","modified":"2013-03-13T09:45:39Z","title":"维权网 | 丁红芬获释后仍受监视，她将申请政府信息公开（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，无锡丁红芬乘坐出租车前往维权人士集结地小花园，一路被一辆牌号为“苏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BG311Y</span><span>”的白色小桥车紧紧跟踪。丁红芬因营救在黑监狱的吴兴国，被当局行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>刚刚获释。她没有来得及恢复健康，就来到小花园揭露黑监狱的黑暗，鼓励拆迁受害人维权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丁红芬因积极维权并帮助暴力拆迁的受害人，为众拆迁户所爱戴，却恼怒了无锡当局，把她视为不安定因素，并在她家对面安装了二个很显眼的摄像头，对她实施全天监视。还配备轿车待命，随时跟踪她。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丁红芬将向国家有关部门申请公开如下政府信息：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、何单位申请在她家对面安装摄像头；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、何机关批准安装该摄像头；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、该摄像头的用途。丁红芬希望政府以书面形式向她公开。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GZKyRN0DhVU/UT_01ky6-_I/AAAAAAAAevM/a0EthBxPrsU/s1600/DSCN2264.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"198\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GZKyRN0DhVU/UT_01ky6-_I/AAAAAAAAevM/a0EthBxPrsU/s320/DSCN2264.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xe7_GXN3kaY/UT_02eckqNI/AAAAAAAAevU/aOznFMcRriI/s1600/DSCN2279.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"208\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xe7_GXN3kaY/UT_02eckqNI/AAAAAAAAevU/aOznFMcRriI/s320/DSCN2279.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-